{"tid":2319197,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"暴動被告准保釋 律政司覆核駁回","createTime":"2020-12-10T02:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T05:40:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6cdb4ee74ec55e96073a3543b5397931fbd619f7","tid":2319197,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:23:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/J2LHON5MHFHIFFSBY6YBZSSUVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FJ2LHON5MHFHIFFSBY6YBZSSUVU%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYplxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=d3b3c15b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FJ2LHON5MHFHIFFSBY6YBZSSUVU%2F&h=224eb29b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/J2LHON5MHFHIFFSBY6YBZSSUVU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n暴動被告准保釋 律政司覆核駁回<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f5SfHtZZy8CH5VHXiyyzsNoaYQI=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WA4HUH2LAFELFBCXPLVPFJYCPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff5SfHtZZy8CH5VHXiyyzsNoaYQI%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWA4HUH2LAFELFBCXPLVPFJYCPY.jpg&h=e5ab1cc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主任裁判官錢禮<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】男子范俊文被控去年七一參與佔領立法會，早前因缺席聆訊而遭法庭發拘捕令，上月底被捕後加控暴動罪，但獲東區法院主任裁判官錢禮批准保釋候訊。錢禮隨即被建制派議員追擊，律政司罕有地向高等法院申請覆核，不滿裁判官批准保釋，要求將范羈押。法官彭寶琴昨聽取控辯雙方陳詞後駁回申請，但收緊保釋條件，包括晚11朝6宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n范俊文（28歲）上月30日在東區法院提堂，由錢禮批准保釋。錢禮早前處理抗爭案件受親建制人士抨。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n律政司長引用《刑事訴訟程序條例》第9H條，申請覆核批准范俊文保釋的決定，要求將范羈押。范原有保釋條件為一萬元保釋金、居於報稱地址、禁足立法會範圍、交出旅遊證件、每兩星期向警署報到一次，父親另提供的一萬元人事擔保。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官令收緊保釋條件<br />\n<br />\n法官彭寶琴拒絕下令范還柙候訊，但增加保釋條件，要求范每晚11時至早上6時守宵禁令，向警署報到加到每周三次，以及由多一人額外提供一萬元人事擔保。范亦須提供僱傭資料和合約副本供法庭作記錄。<br />\n<br />\n佔領立法會。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCCP723/20"},{"pid":"a174cc0e4930df5102c5548e511a960543bd4a16","tid":2319197,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:27:02.000Z","msg":"睇嚟連愛党愛警嘅彭寶琴都要準備俾班紅藍喪屍追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf5db4176de36bf6de47c661935e7e576ebf669","tid":2319197,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"我好奇點解今次又准保釋？"},{"pid":"6b62aefd9ec6a9c5e7599a576cc3c6ad9fd56674","tid":2319197,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bf5db4176de36bf6de47c661935e7e576ebf669","tid":2319197,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"我好奇點解今次又准保釋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T02:34:32.000Z","msg":"佢本身係收唔到傳票,唔係刻意唔上庭,呢個情況基本上都會批保釋"},{"pid":"cacb0fae8f342fce77c9bb92797dbc7e3ee1b9a0","tid":2319197,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T03:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f9d7eb00a47f036f341df235dba2093a774da8","tid":2319197,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"正常官"},{"pid":"04b357672b33236f57a50aaca13f707987e77629","tid":2319197,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61f9d7eb00a47f036f341df235dba2093a774da8","tid":2319197,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"正常官"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}